content.rendered:
In the days leading up to the 1988 Seoul Olympics, an undercover team of drivers and mechanics secretly tries to dismantle a money-laundering gang.

Directed By Hyun-Sung Moon

Written By Sua Shin

Stars: Yoo Ah-in. Go Kyung-Pyo. Andrew Grace
